These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: apricot, coral
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-milk
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is not the person who likes coral##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | coral   | apricot  |
| Sport   | lemonade | almond-milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
City: new-york, venice
The people have 2 different jobs:  firefighter, security-guard
1. the firefighter is on the left of the security-guard##1
2. the firefighter is not the person traveling to venice##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | new-york | venice      |
| Pet    | firefighter  | security-guard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, june
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: iris, poppy
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who growsiris is not the person who's birthday is in december##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |
| Food    | june  | december    |
| Sport   | iris | poppy |

